{"tid":843174,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬球迷打比戰中高喊C朗名字","createTime":"2018-10-01T03:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T09:14:22.000Z","uid":25345,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5e8d8dfc87d6af64b68265268d497f060294c1d6","tid":843174,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://crawl.nosdn.127.net/5fe18f3f8735961811f5c949355dfa3a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.nosdn.127.net%2F5fe18f3f8735961811f5c949355dfa3a.png&h=fc83c146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://crawl.nosdn.127.net/c0624391e22d921204a152e441eaf638.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcrawl.nosdn.127.net%2Fc0624391e22d921204a152e441eaf638.jpg&h=583c5e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《每日鏡報》報道，在皇馬悶平馬競的德比戰中，皇馬球迷高喊C羅的名字。<br />\n<br />\n本場比賽皇馬有7次射正，但沒有取得進球，和馬競0-0戰平。<br />\n<br />\n球隊遲遲無法取得進球，皇馬球迷很是擔憂和焦急，他們高唱&ldquo;羅納爾多，羅納爾多&rdquo;，表示對這位俱樂部歷史最佳射手的懷念。<br />\n<br />\nC羅438場比賽為皇馬打進驚人的451球，今夏轉會尤文圖斯，在尤文擊敗那不勒斯的比賽中獨造3球，威猛無比。<br />\n<br />\n《鏡報》稱皇馬球迷也曾噓過C羅，但他們現在的呼喚已經太晚了。"},{"pid":"bb57dd82fba60fb8ae0f0d8e8d7f795e9cb6108f","tid":843174,"uid":24362,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:19:30.000Z","msg":"牙朗俾錢請人做show姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bee4ea66179ee39ec46779a0bef219a36a1e7f9","tid":843174,"uid":90515,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:21:16.000Z","msg":"一黎唔係十二碼<br />\n二種唔係門前撞入<br />\n<br />\n召喚到阿朗都無用啦"},{"pid":"4c7dbee2b26cd9c329509fff976b52134ac49a7c","tid":843174,"uid":90515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一黎唔係十二碼<br />\n二黎唔係門前撞入<br />\n<br />\n召喚到阿朗都無用啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"49a5ffeaeb7678a0c8b4949dd5a206bf48cec087","tid":843174,"uid":4622,"like":23,"dislike":4,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https:/